<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 items-stretch">
    <!-- Left: Text Content -->
    <div class="flex flex-col justify-center md:col-span-2">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-gray-900 mb-8">
        Need To Scale Your Roofing Company With More Qualified Leads?
      </h2>

      <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-rebel-green mb-8">
        Done Relying On Referrals To Keep Your Calendar Full?
      </h3>

      <div class="space-y-6 text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          You do quality work. Your customers are happy. You get referrals. But when those referrals dry up, your calendar gets thin. Meanwhile, your competitors show up first on Google even though you do better work. You've tried agencies before—they made big promises, delivered mediocre results, and blamed your market when their campaigns failed. Or they built you a nice-looking website that doesn't generate a single lead.
        </p>

        <p>
          Here's the truth: a website alone doesn't work. Google Ads alone don't work. SEO alone doesn't work. You need a complete system where everything works together—website, ads, local SEO, tracking, and continuous optimization. That's what actually generates predictable revenue.
        </p>

        <p class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">
          Most agencies sell you services. <span class="text-rebel-green">We build you systems.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Right: Image -->
    <div class="flex items-stretch">
      <img
        src="https://RebelApeCDN.b-cdn.net/featured-google-business-profile-for-plumbers-office.webp"
        alt="Google Business Profile example"
        class="w-full h-full object-cover rounded-lg shadow-xl"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</div>